### AI Disruption Analysis\
\
**Purpose**: Help users understand AI's impact on their chosen careers\
\
**Risk Levels**:\
- **Low**: Human-centered skills (therapy, teaching, creative work)\
- **Medium**: Mixed automation potential (development, design, writing)\
- **High**: High automation potential (data entry, routine analysis)\
\
**Provides**:\
- Automation risk assessment\
- Future outlook\
- Adaptation recommendations\
- AI literacy pathways\
\
**Example Output**:\
```\
Career: UX Designer\
AI Risk Level: Low-Medium\
Description: Core human skills remain essential\
Recommendations:\
- Learn AI-assisted design tools\
- Focus on user empathy and research\
- Develop strategic thinking skills\
```\
