## Troubleshooting\
\
### User Feels Overwhelmed\
- Slow down pace\
- Use reset routine\
- Break content into smaller chunks\
- Offer more check-ins\
\
### User Stuck on Module\
- Revisit previous work\
- Offer alternative approaches\
- Provide additional examples\
- Connect with peer support\
\
### User Losing Motivation\
- Reconnect with goals\
- Celebrate progress so far\
- Adjust expectations\
- Explore interests more deeply\
